  "id": "019d286c-c8e3-7462-a4e5-9d0ab5d156c1",
  "content": "\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-green);\">~1 GB</span><br>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted);\">OS only, Docker adds minimal</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <table class=\"comparison-table\">\n    <tr>\n      <th>Feature</th>\n      <th>Windows</th>\n      <th>WSL2</th>\n      <th>Native Linux</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Docker overhead</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-red);\">Hyper-V VM</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-amber);\">Lightweight VM</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-green);\">Native kernel</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px;\">File I/O speed</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-red);\">Slow (cross-FS)</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-amber);\">Fast in /home</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-green);\">Native speed</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GPU passthrough</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-amber);\">Limited</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-amber);\">CUDA yes, Vulkan partial</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-green);\">Full access</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Memory reclaim</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-red);\">OS controls</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-amber);\">Can leak (vmmem)</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-green);\">Full control</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <div class=\"insight-box\">\n    <p>Devcontainers on WSL2 work, but Windows + WSL VM eats RAM before<br>\n    your container even starts. On native Linux, <strong>Docker talks directly<br>\n    to the kernel</strong> &mdash; no VM tax, no memory leaks.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">04 / 08</div>\n</div>",
